{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"向幸福进军的人们","authors":["孙俊","高庆赓"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":28}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"向幸福进军的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙俊诗  高庆赓摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原春光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原上的春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴制度已被埋葬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千亩良田归人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又收回成群的牛羊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶变成主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲啼变成欢畅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给高原带来了永恒的春光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活在欢乐中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人们带来了欢乐的生活；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多年被奴役的“朗生”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有了自己的归宿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看他俩多么亲密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看他俩多么快乐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在赶走贫困的同时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又奏起攀登文化高峰的战歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前姑娘愁到了眉尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天姑娘喜到了心窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的一张动人的笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一首青春的颂歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她憧憬着美好的未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她歌唱着幸福的生活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳是她的优美的本性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愉快是社会主义给她的战果！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心连着心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你让我们脱离苦海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你使我们走向光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的祖国呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和你心连着心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读报组是我们的课堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它传播着你的跃进的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的藏族儿女啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你的成就感到无比自豪的欢欣！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}